{"title":"[数据结构]点的距离","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1161#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=1161","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1161/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1161/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/1161"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"给定一棵有n个结点的树，Q 个询问，每次询问点x到点y两点之间的距离。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个n，表示这棵树有n个结点。接下来n−1行，每行两个整数x,y表示x,y之间有一条连边。然后一个整数Q，表示有Q个询问，接下来Q行每行两个整数x,y表示询问x到y的距离。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出 Q 行，每行表示每个询问的答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入示例\r\n```\r\n6\r\n1 2\r\n1 3\r\n2 4\r\n2 5\r\n3 6\r\n2\r\n2 6\r\n5 6\r\n```\r\n输出示例\r\n```\r\n3\r\n4\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"数据范围：1<=n<=10e5, 1<=x,y<=n"}]}